Victoire CMS {{ theme }} {{ widget }} Theme Bundle
============

This bundle is a theme for the widget {{ widget }}.
To use this theme, you must have this widget installed in a Victoire project.

Then you just have to run the following composer command in your projet :

    php composer.phar require victoire/{{ theme|lower }}-bundle

Do not forget to add the bundle in your AppKernel !

    class AppKernel extends Kernel
    {
        public function registerBundles()
        {
            $bundles = array(
                ...
                new {{ namespace }}\{{ bundle }}(),
            );

            return $bundles;
        }
    }

